trans-unit.source: Contains forest trust account information about a top-level domain in a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" />.
trans-unit.target: 包含與 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> 中的最上層網域有關的樹系信任帳戶資訊。

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of a top-level domain in a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" />.
trans-unit.target: 取得 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> 中的最上層網域名稱。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the name of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelName" /> object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.String" />，其中包含 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelName" /> 物件的名稱。

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the status of a top-level domain in a <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" />.
trans-unit.target: 取得或設定 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest" /> 中最上層網域的狀態。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameStatus" /> value that contains the status of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelName" /> object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameStatus" /> 值，其中包含 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelName" /> 物件的狀態。

trans-unit.source: The value is not one of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameStatus" /> values.
trans-unit.target: 該值不是其中一個 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TopLevelNameStatus" /> 值。
